headline: FIS Expands Auto Market Presence with Cloud-based Asset Finance Solution
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., November 18, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial technology, today announced a major SaaS-based cloud offering enhancement to its FIS Asset Finance solution.
